Enum Rank

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Rank>
com.github.bhlangonijr.chesslib.Rank
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Rank>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum Rank extends Enum<Rank>
The ranks in a board. A rank is a raw in the chessboard, and it is identified as a number from 1 to 8.

Each value defines a single rank, except for the special value NONE which represents no rank.
